* Forms beginning with {{lang|ja|だ}} or {{lang|ja|で}}: From the particle {{ja-r|で}} or {{ja-r|である|rom=de aru}}. The lemma form {{lang|ja|だ}} itself is a contraction of {{lang|ja|であ}}, clipping of {{m|ja|である|tr=de aru}}.
